        "text" : "Pleasure! And most in class were engaged with your work as it was one of the required reading! Thank you and yes, working for a PhD - started in Sep so at a very early stage but I'm finding myself pulling away from the traditional analytic philosophy towards the embodied, enaction approaches... hope all is well with you.",
