        "text" : "yep, still standing. Couldn‚Äôt get to China for now, so still in Edinburgh. Hoping to be back there in July/August, in time for birth of our baby early September. Then all three of us relocate back here to the UK (assuming the pandemic is actually resolved by then....)",
