        "text" : "Thanks Ricky! That seems to have worked. If you've any suggestions for people the kids could contact, I'd be grateful. I'm not completely sure they'll take up the opportunity -- they can be shy -- but I think Harry at least would be up for it. He's 15 and loves meeting new people.",
