        "text" : "That's great news Helen! (Ruth came up with the basic Swampman idea of course; it's an illustration of her view not an objection.) Your book is going to be terrific; I'm looking forward to seeing it. \nRe BL: I'm not a fan, and I've never interacted with him before, but I thought I'd give it a try, partly as an experiment :)",
