  "dmConversation" : {
    "conversationId" : "50668170-52522040",
    "messages" : [ {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "but then, I am like my dad and so are you, so that makes sense\n",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "334084705773314049",
        "createdAt" : "2013-05-13T23:16:15.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "thank heavens you are like me!",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "334084579226959873",
        "createdAt" : "2013-05-13T23:15:45.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "50668170",
        "text" : "We'd love it too! Just let us when you'd like to visit. But you'd have to excuse our disorganized lifestyle &amp; wild children :)",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "52522040",
        "id" : "334084346355007488",
        "createdAt" : "2013-05-13T23:14:49.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "I would love that! That is such a generous offer, Keith",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "334079764451164161",
        "createdAt" : "2013-05-13T22:56:37.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "50668170",
        "text" : "I'd be proud to think I resembled your dad. I hope you'll come and visit us some time and tell us more about him.",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "52522040",
        "id" : "334079456501186561",
        "createdAt" : "2013-05-13T22:55:23.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "Thank you for being the lovely warm and caring person that you are, Keith, you always reminded me of my dad, and that makes me smile",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "334076844750016512",
        "createdAt" : "2013-05-13T22:45:01.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "50668170",
        "text" : "I never met him but I feel how fantastic he was - and he'll go on making people feel that. I'm sending you a big hug Saskia { }",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "52522040",
        "id" : "334073741984272384",
        "createdAt" : "2013-05-13T22:32:41.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "came. He thanked her profusely for doing this for us, she was moved too. It was so right, but I will miss him so terribly, my fantastic dad",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "334066248583352322",
        "createdAt" : "2013-05-13T22:02:54.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "peaceful. We were all together when he got the lethal injections. We hugged and even joked around a bit, like my father is, until the doctor",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "334065936254509056",
        "createdAt" : "2013-05-13T22:01:40.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "dear Keith, your words mean such a lot to me. He will live on in my heart, I loved him so dearly, and the departure was so warm and ...",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "334065553637507072",
        "createdAt" : "2013-05-13T22:00:09.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "50668170",
        "text" : "So sorry to hear your news Saskia. An unmeasurable loss, but he is still with you in so many ways. Much love from Maria and me.",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "52522040",
        "id" : "334062784620929024",
        "createdAt" : "2013-05-13T21:49:09.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "his hands barely work anymore because of the polyneuropathy. He's written a lot though, he will not leave us with emptiness ",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "246123356083081216",
        "createdAt" : "2012-09-13T05:49:15.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "50668170",
        "text" : "I'm sure I'd like your father very much. Has he considered sharing his thoughts and feelings through a blog?",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "52522040",
        "id" : "245997853506408448",
        "createdAt" : "2012-09-12T21:30:33.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "And you'd definitely like my dad, he's a cool calm and collected guy with very outspoken and well thought of opinions :)",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "245633688585510912",
        "createdAt" : "2012-09-11T21:23:29.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "Dear Keith, you are such a gem, thank you for your kind and thoughtful words, and your warm consideration and concern. I am moved.",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "245633435505397760",
        "createdAt" : "2012-09-11T21:22:29.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "thank you so much, Keith. It is such a strange thing. He is ok with it himslf, that helps.",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "245417646068215808",
        "createdAt" : "2012-09-11T07:05:01.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "50668170",
        "text" : "Thinking of you Saskia. I hope your dad's remaining time is good. Everyone's time is limited &amp; it's quality that matters.&lt;Hugs&gt;",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "52522040",
        "id" : "245303113219719168",
        "createdAt" : "2012-09-10T23:29:54.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "50668170",
        "text" : "I understand how that feels (my parents are still with us, but old now). Enjoy every minute of your time together.",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "52522040",
        "id" : "198533086777057281",
        "createdAt" : "2012-05-04T22:02:31.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "thank you, Keith. It was one of the roughest things, to wave goodbye to dad and think it was the last time? but here he is!",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "198530128488316929",
        "createdAt" : "2012-05-04T21:50:45.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "Dear Keith, late reply due to bad 3G here in France, camping. Thanks for your warm thoughts, it is so appreciated, things are tough.",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "3797284056",
        "createdAt" : "2011-08-09T21:17:40.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "50668170",
        "text" : "Hi Saskia. Just wanted to say hi & see how you & yr parents are. Focus on the good things & I'm sure you'll all gain strength. Best wishes,K",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "52522040",
        "id" : "3748677470",
        "createdAt" : "2011-08-04T14:40:58.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "Thank you so much Keith, it was just so tough already, and we thought we could take stock and move on. It's just too much.",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "50668170",
        "id" : "3658567828",
        "createdAt" : "2011-07-27T08:44:49.000Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "50668170",
        "text" : "Thinking of you and your parents. Stay positive and help your dad to be positive too. It does help. Warmest wishes, Keith.",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "52522040",
        "id" : "3651823552",
        "createdAt" : "2011-07-26T23:13:05.000Z"
      }
    } ]
  }
