        "text" : "Hi Ema -- Yes I did get it. Sorry for the delay in replying -- I've a backlog of email waiting for me! Thank you for the invitation. The volume looks great, and I'd like to contribute -- especially if you won't need final drafts till mid-2020. (I've a lot of writing commitments for 2019.) Would something on thought insertion and occurrent belief be suitable? All best wishes for the new year!",
