    "conversationId" : "52522040-72796877",
    "messages" : [ {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "72796877",
        "text" : "David -- I've posted a reply to your comment on my blog post. It's just me thinking aloud, but it may help you to see how I think about this -- and perhaps identify where I go wrong!  Don't feel obliged to reply -- though of course I'd love to know what you think. (Or, if you'd prefer to do this privately by email, do please say so.) All best wishes from a dark and chilly Crete. Keith",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "52522040",
        "id" : "1220456236728180745",
        "createdAt" : "2020-01-23T21:20:16.527Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "72796877",
        "text" : "Thanks David. No worries at all. I always take your comments seriously since I've enormous respect for you and think you are right about most things. By the same token, please don't take anything I say on Twitter too seriously. I use it as a way of thinking aloud and trying out ideas and ways of putting things. (It's also a good way of keeping in touch with people, given my current geographical isolation.) \n\nI'm still not quite sure exactly where you differ from Dan and me on consciousness. It would be great to talk to you about it some time. Best wishes, K",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "52522040",
        "id" : "1195714911890006020",
        "createdAt" : "2019-11-16T14:47:05.006Z"
      }
    }, {
      "messageCreate" : {
        "recipientId" : "52522040",
        "text" : "Keith I hope you don‚Äôt mind that I‚Äôm jumping on you like this. I think your position is very interesting which is why I‚Äôm getting involved. But do say if you‚Äôre not having fun. D",
        "mediaUrls" : [ ],
        "senderId" : "72796877",
        "id" : "1195708495296905220",
        "createdAt" : "2019-11-16T14:21:35.171Z"
      }
    } ]
